<!-- AccuGeo Liner demo website: conversion of www.accugeo.com (subset) to the GrowERP
     'modern' template set, per docs/Website_Template_Definition.md.
     Demonstrates: light theme (luminaBrightness "light"), grouped navbar dropdowns from
     nested pagePaths (products/*, applications/*), and a hidden page (_ path segment).
     Self-contained: organization + contacts, product store, hostname mapping, wiki content, theme.
     Load explicitly (not part of seed/install):
        java -jar moqui.war load location=component://growerp/data/AccuGeoDemoData.xml no-run-es
     Notes:
     - Subset of the ~46 source pages: home, about, contact, 3 products, 3 applications,
       1 hidden spec page. Remaining pages follow the same pattern.
     - The organization has no GrowERP owner (ownerPartyId), so it does not appear in any
       tenant's admin app; this file exists to serve the public website only.
     - No images scraped; product photos can be uploaded later via the Website dialog. -->
