        <file mimeType="text/html" versionName="01" rootVersionName="01">
            <fileData><![CDATA[<#-- title: PVC -->
<main class="pt-28 pb-16">
    <section class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 md:px-12 py-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">PVC Liners</h1>
        <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-5 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            <p>
                PVC is durable and easy to use, making it a perfect liner for beginners. Adhesive
                will seam and patch PVC and requires no expensive equipment.
            </p>
            <p>
                PVC liners should be buried, the same as PVC pipe. PVC has carbon black as a UV
                inhibitor, however prolonged UV exposure will degrade PVC over time. Buried PVC
                liners will have a life of 20 years or more. Exposed PVC liners last a few months to
                a year, depending on the thickness of the liner.
            </p>
            <p>
                PVC roll stock is 7.083 feet wide. After subtracting for the seam, the width of the
                liner panels will be in increments of 7'. For example, a panel could be 14' wide or
                21' wide, etc. The maximum panel width is 140'. The length can be any value.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="l-glass rounded-2xl p-8 mt-10 max-w-3xl">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-on-surface mb-4">At a glance</h2>
            <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-sm">
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Standard thicknesses</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">10, 20, 30, 40, 60 mil</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Panel width increments</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">7' (max 140')</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Seaming methods</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">RF welding, heat welding, adhesive</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Standard warranty</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">20 years when buried (not on 10 mil)</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Minimum order</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">None</dd></div>
            </dl>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/content/products/_pvc-spec" class="l-glass hover:bg-surface-container-high/60 text-on-surface font-label text-sm font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">description</span>
                PVC specification sheet
            </a>
            <a href="/content/contact" class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-on-primary font-label text-sm font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg l-glow transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                Get a quote
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>]]></fileData>
