            <fileData><![CDATA[<#-- title: HDPE -->
<main class="pt-28 pb-16">
    <section class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 md:px-12 py-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">HDPE Liners</h1>
        <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-5 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            <p>
                HDPE (High Density Polyethylene) is a special form of polyethylene that has longer
                carbon strings with less branching. The result is a more compactable molecule and a
                higher density. HDPE is available smooth or with texturing called Microspike&reg; to
                increase the slip coefficient.
            </p>
            <p>
                HDPE is shipped in large rolls and mechanically deployed. All seams are made in the
                field using heat fusion or a tape designed for geosynthetics. HDPE is slightly less
                expensive than other materials, but has a higher cost of installation. It can be
                cost effective in large projects. HDPE should only be installed by qualified
                professionals.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="l-glass rounded-2xl p-8 mt-10 max-w-3xl">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-on-surface mb-4">At a glance</h2>
            <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-sm">
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Standard thicknesses</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">12, 20, 30, 40, 60, 80, 100 mil</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Roll width</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">19' (12&ndash;20 mil), 23' (other)</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Seaming methods</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">Heat welding, tape</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Standard warranty</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">1 year, extensions available</dd></div>
                <div><dt class="text-outline font-label">Minimum order</dt><dd class="text-on-surface">None</dd></div>
            </dl>
            <p class="text-xs text-outline mt-4">Microspike&reg; is a registered trademark of Agru America, Inc.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="/content/contact" class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-on-primary font-label text-sm font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg l-glow transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                Get a quote
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>]]></fileData>
