        <file mimeType="text/markdown" versionName="01" rootVersionName="01">
            <fileData><![CDATA[# PVC Specification Sheet

Reference values for AccuGeo fabricated PVC geomembrane liners.

## Material

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Material | Polyvinyl chloride (PVC), carbon black UV inhibitor |
| Standard thicknesses | 10, 20, 30, 40, 60 mil (1 mil = 1/1000 inch) |
| Roll stock width | 7.083 ft |
| Panel width increments | 7 ft |
| Maximum panel width | 140 ft |
| Maximum panel weight | ideally under 6,000 lbs |

## Fabrication

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Seaming methods | RF welding, heat welding, adhesive |
| Recommended installation | buried, like PVC pipe |
| Service life (buried) | 20 years or more |
| Service life (exposed) | months to a year, thickness dependent |

## Commercial

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Standard warranty | 20 years when buried (not offered on 10 mil) |
| Minimum order quantity | none |

Back to the [PVC product page](/content/products/pvc).]]></fileData>
